column12: Surgical retractor assembly having tissue viability sensor embedded therein
column13: A surgical retractor is disclosed having a generally flat malleable blade with a miniature metabolic parameter sensor embedded or removably inset into the blade. The sensor detects physiologic and metabolic parameters to monitor tissue viability of the tissue underlying the retractor.
